  "text": "We remind that astrophysical and heavy-ion plasmas require relativistic extensions of the q-formalism [CITATION_1] . The reader might be also interested to some recent applications of nonextensive statistical mechanics, where a physical meaning of q is introduced: to astrophysics by Jiulin and Yeli (2008a,2008b) to heavy ions by Wilk and collaborators [CITATION_2] .",
